K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-1: sta na ma h'a da ra panytsa /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-3: 'bras bu chen po lnga bsgral ba'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-4: dpal chen khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-5: mi phyed dang bas phyag 'tshal na //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-6: de nas sta na'i lung bshad de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-7: ye nas rgyu nyid dag pa las //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-8: nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-9: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyu ru gyur //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-10: khams gsum de dag bsgral ba'i zhing //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-11: a'a sa ma ca la dharma dha tu sva bha ba a'atma ko nya ham/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-12: ram yam kham ta tha phat/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal to //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-14: mi g-yo phyag rgya chen po'i dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-15: dbang ph yug chen po'i bsgral thabs ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-16: 'tsho ba'i bdag po'i tshe dang srog /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-17: thugs rje'i ngang dang shes rab dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-18: thabs la mkhas pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-19: 'gro ba thams cad sbyong bar mdzad //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-20: bdud dang gshin rje 'khor bcas kun //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-21: gnyis med phyag rgyar rol pa yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-22: dus la bab po sa ma ya //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:307b-23: aom sarba p'a pa ka he ha sa si stam/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-1: ma tang gi ni rnam shes de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-2: nges par gzugs la bab nas ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-3: ta ki zhal ni nub tu bstan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-4: dbang du bsdu ba'i las mdzad kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-5: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis rlob //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-6: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba'i zhing //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-7: sta na chen po bya ba'i phyir //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-8: bder gshegs mang po kun 'dus shing //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-9: byams dang snying rje ldan pa yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-10: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgya dral te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-11: gnas kyi sgo 'di su yis bcad //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-12: sems kyi bdag pos bcad dam ci //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-13: gzung 'dzin rkang pa bsnol ba yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-14: yul las 'das pa'i sgo phye zhig ces brjod de sgo dbye'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-15: ka ta ri ka na pra be sha /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-16: g-yon pa'i zhabs kyis ru tra'i gzugs //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-17: gnas kyi sgo 'di bcad bzhin du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-18: bde bar gshegs pa'i skyabs su gsol //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-19: shi ba'i sdug bsngal 'dir byung ngo //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-20: zhes lha chen po brgyad kyis dus gcig tu tshig de smras so //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-21: ta ki brgyad kyis bka' stsal pa //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-22: dregs pa ma rungs lha chen khyod //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-23: sems kyi sgo kun de dbye yi //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-24: rdo rje 'bar ba'i spu gri yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-25: gnas kyi sgo kun de phye nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-26: sems kyis bdag pos gzung bar bya //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-28: skye ba'i rkyen gyis 'chi ba yin; ;sdig pa'i rkyen gyis bcom pas 'chi //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-29: bdag kyang dngos por lta bas 'jig /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308a-30: nga yi bstan pa 'di la gzung //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-0: gzugs 'dzin @308b rkang lag yul las bzlas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-1: pho mo bsnol te mnan pa yang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-2: mgo ni lho nub mtshams su bsnan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-3: rkang pa byang shar mtshams su brkyang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-4: ta ki'i zhabs ni g-yas pa yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-5: ru tra ling+ga'i steng du mnan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-6: de ltar ling+ga mnan byas na //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-7: thar byed chen po'i 'gying stabs kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-8: rngam brjid chen pos 'di skad do //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-9: sa ma ya ke sha tsi ta dzva la h'um phat/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-10: ces mnan no; ;ma h'a de ba ru tra dza zhes pa dang /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-11: khams gsum nas 'byung sems can rnams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-12: rdo rje sku yi khyad par gyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-13: 'od zer tshul du bsdus nas ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-14: de dag bdag gis gzugs la gzung //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-15: spro ba rdo rje thams cad kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-16: sku dang ye shes mchog gis bya'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-18: brod pa can rnams 'ong ba ltar //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-19: skal dang ldan pa rigs kyi bu //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-21: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-22: rtse rgyal bstan pa'i gnas chen 'dir //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-23: bo dhi tsitta'i dbyings nyid du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-25: chos nyid skye 'gag med pa la //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-26: bde bar gshegs dang 'gro ba zhes //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-27: dbyings su gcig pas gnyis su med //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-28: kun kyang ngo bo mnyam nyid de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-29: thams cad snying po byang chub sems //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-31: bdag nyid med na mnyam pa'i sku //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-32: thugs rje chen po cir mi mdzad //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:308b-33: ye gnas de ltar de bzhin du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-0: @309a *// sems can ma rig rmongs pa'i blos //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-1: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-2: rtag chad mtha' gnyis ma spangs te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-3: nor bas btags pa'i phung po lnga //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-4: log rtog phyin ci log bzhis bcings //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-5: nyon mongs sdug bsngal rgyu bsags te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-6: 'khor ba'i rgyud lnga kha brims pas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-7: mya ngan mi 'da' yun ring ste //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-8: phung po khams dang skye mched la //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-9: 'khrul pa'i phag chags bag la nyal //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-10: bde 'gro'i lam la bsgribs pa rnams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-11: 'khor ba'i lam lnga rgyun gcad phyir //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-12: ngan song rnam par sbyong ba'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-13: ma ta ma ta sarba pre ta ga te he tum h'um phat/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-14: pa tsa pa tsa sarba ti ra ya he tum phat/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-15: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga te he tum h'um phat/
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-16: de ltar ngan song rnams sbyangs te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-17: sdug bsngal gsum gyi sgo bcad phyir //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-18: ram ya kham zhes brjod la /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-19: ye shes 'bar ba'i mes bsregs te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-20: mtshan nyid med par stong par 'gyur //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-21: dus la bab pa'i sems can de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-22: las la bab pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-24: thugs rje lcags kyus bkug nas ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-25: skal dang ldan pa'i rnam shes des //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-26: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-27: sku yi sprul pa phyogs bcur bkye //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-28: gsung gis sems can mtha' dag grol //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-29: thugs ni tshad med bzhi dang ldan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309a-30: nyi zla gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-0: tshe dpag @309b med par dbang bskur nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-1: yang dag nyid la yang dag sgrol //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-2: yang dag bsgral na bde chen thob //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-3: mi ldog sa la nges par phyin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-4: phyin pa tsam gyis dbang thob nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-5: rgyal ba'i zhing khams dbyings nyid mthong //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-6: rgyu drug gnas su mi skye phyir //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-7: dpa' bo 'bru lngas lam lnga dgag /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-9: 'og min dga' ldan lha yul du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-10: ye shes rlung gis brten nas ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-11: sbyor ba'i lhums su phat gyis 'phang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-12: aa nri su tri pri du /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-13: gang yang rung ba'i rnam shes de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-14: gsang ba'i dbyings su h'um gis bsdu //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-15: skur bskyed ye shes skur spros te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-16: dbyings dang ye shes lhun grub pas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-17: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-18: bde gshegs pho brang dkyil 'khor du //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-19: rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan pa yis; ;'phags pa'i lam du rlung zhugs nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-20: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing gshegs //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-21: 'jig rten lha yi gtso bo dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-22: nyan thos dgra bcom rang rgyal dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-23: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-25: stug pos brgyan pa'i sa 'das nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-26: padma spyan gyi sa la gzhag /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-27: 'chi ba med pa'i chos sku thob //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-28: stong gsum ma lus bton pa bas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-29: 'bum gyi char yang mi phod de //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-30: rang sems ma bcos ye nas chub //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:309b-31: skyes bu chen po rnal 'byor gyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-0: bsgral ba 'ba' zhig snying rje'i mchog @310a *//
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-1: de nas ma trang ru tra de bsgral te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-2: sngon byung ba yi gleng gzhi dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-3: gtan tshigs su dgongs nas phyi rabs kyi sngags 'chang
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-4: rnams yid ches par bya ba dang dad pa can
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-5: gyi rnal 'byor pa rnams drang ba'i phyir dur khrod
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-7: ma mo chen po brgyad dang /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-8: rang byung gi mchod rten chen po brgyad /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-9: 'di man chang gtan tshigs dang bcas te bstan to //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-10: gong du bsgral ba'i bsam rgyud ni /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-12: 'di yang bsnor te lung dkyus nas bstan no //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-13: bdud dang dbang phyug gshin rje de; ;thugs rje tshad med bzhis bsgral nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-14: ro yi nyal thabs gan rkyal te //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-15: dzambu gling lo'i gling khams su //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-16: bor nas sa gzhir gyur pa ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-17: dur khrod chen po brgyad du gyur //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-18: mgo ni lho nub mtshams su bstan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-19: rkang pa byang shar mtshams su bstan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-20: lag pa gnyis ni g-yas g-yon brkyang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-21: mgo dang lus snying yan lag kun //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-22: gnas kyi dur khrod chen po brgyad //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-23: de ni dpal chen bzhugs gnas yin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-24: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-25: ro yi srung mchen mo ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-26: ma mo chen mo brgyad gzhag go /
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-27: de yi gnas rten chen por yang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-28: mchod rten chen po gzi byin can //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-29: rang byung re re bzhag pa yin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-30: de ltar sa gzhi 'di kun yang //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310a-31: bkra shis ya mtshan thugs rje can //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-0: chos dang @310b dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-2: de yi lus snying ma ga ta //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-3: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-4: ma mo chen mo ke'u ri gnas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-5: mkhas shing snying stobs che ba'i sa'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-6: mchod rten ming ni bde byed rten //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-7: de yi mgo bo lho phyogs kyi //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-8: dur khrod chen po bzhag pa ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-9: sing+ga yul gyi gling phran yin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-10: ma mo chen mo tse'u ri gnas //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-11: mthong thos rnam pa'i 'phrul bag can //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-12: mchod rten ri bo ta la la //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-13: lag pa g-yas pa shar lho'i mtshams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-14: dur khrod chen po bal yul yin //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-15: ma mo chen mo pukka si //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-16: lhag par zas kyi longs spyod che //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-17: mchod rten kha sho by'a ghri kha'o //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-18: lag pa g-yon ni lho nub mtshams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-19: dur khrod chen po sa la'i yul //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-20: ma mo chen mo be t'a li //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-21: phyag na rdo rje dbang gi gnas; ;de ni mthu dang dbang yang che //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-22: gyad yul chen po'i sa las ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-23: mchod rten ma la sa ganda //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-24: rkang pa g-yas pa byang shar mtshams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-25: dur khrod chen po li yi yul //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-26: ma mo chen mo tsanda li //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-27: lha mo shang ki ni zhes grags //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-28: chu dang me grub rdzu 'phrul can //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-29: mchod rten ming ni ge'u to shan //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-30: rkang pa g-yon ba nub byang mtshams //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-31: dur khrod chen po kha che'i yul //
K12D0841(1-8)-4_H0805-4:310b-32: ma mo chen mo pra mo ha //
